Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国的由麻粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你要等到什么时候才变身啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「难道那只是CospIay吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「用片头曲骗人」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这般指责的屈辱日子到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 由麻我终于当上了退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说 很久以前起我就是退魔少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 快看 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我可是吃了一番苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我来为大家介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两位便是我的神 小空和小海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小缠还是不太想当退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.27,0:01:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以往后由我来代替她消灭恶灵 维护和平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 干脆把标题也改了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其名为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还蹬鼻子上脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻和高次元体「同调」了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 你能看到由麻的高次元体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个小女孩神和一个小男孩神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸小空和狸猫小海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美诠释了东洋的奥秘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这趟日本来得值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也觉得？你也觉得？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时和两个同调？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说两个合起来才是一个高次元体？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时神器已经召出了高次元体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且已经使用过它的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没有对探测器起反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然同一时期出现两个缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种巧合…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己建了一个退魔少女网站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4\fax-0.18\frz352.7\pos(563.733,716.267)}消灭恶灵 保护小镇的和平!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.18\frz352.7\pos(798.4,835)}为灵烦恼的人请联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs42\fax-0.05\frz349\frx0\fry0\pos(644.4,807.6)}肩膀突然变沉了 真让人头疼\N请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候建的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话音刚落 祛除恶灵的委托就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三巷的森田说肩膀突然变得很沉 正在犯愁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是被恶灵附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是肩膀酸痛而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我网站上的那个一摸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 退魔少女出动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 森田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然出现了第二个缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是一对高次元体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把草薙由麻也纳入监视对象 继续监视
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜把「信条杀手」都派过来的奈兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何会在那之后毫无动静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是冲皇缠的雷加利亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说有其他目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附在森田上的居然不是恶灵而是肩周炎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就跟你说是误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来新的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\frz338.4\pos(878,580)}想请您帮忙驱邪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们准备建房子 想请您驱邪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的不是这个「驱邪」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做奠基仪式的话 请联系天万神社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz346.8\pos(1242,627)}墓地里有地缚灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一个普通墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz25.16\pos(1258,375)}发现UFO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UFO？ 在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人不归我管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\frz21.67\pos(1356,475)}退魔少女快来!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 是退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我签名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的 你们排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 这里是釜谷警署恶性犯罪调查科
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店街的玩偶装被幽灵附身了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位太太 警察不处理这类案件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别偷懒 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子是当时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是原宿警署吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是釜谷警署恶性犯罪调查科的巡查部长皇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她彻底蔫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟和奈兹有关的事件并没有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我怎么一周之内被卷进去3次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己太特殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点自知之明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我想要普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 没有恶灵就说明很太平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委托来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釜谷商业街的「釜吉」被幽灵附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs46}恭喜您设立了退魔活动用网站\N请恕我唐突 这里联络您是有时想委托您\N釜谷商业街的「釜吉」被幽灵附身了\N请您帮忙祛除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您帮忙祛除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釜吉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釜谷市的地方吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得通俗说 就是这块土地的形象人物的玩偶装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是赶时髦才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但设计有点那个 根本没有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这个情报是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天没有雕具座的门被打开的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有可能是在我来这个国家之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹就附在穿着玩偶装的人的身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该我们退魔少女出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候成你的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我也算进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们去看釜吉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样很快就能知道是否真有恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所谓百闻不如一见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 为什么要摆出一脸不情愿的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有退魔少女该有的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我一个人去看看釜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小空 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人不太想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你在害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我由麻的搭档竟然害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样也算是男孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严格来说是高次元体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是拖我也要把你拖去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为了我能作为退魔少女闪亮出道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在没法不管她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釜吉不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明平时都在这条商业街的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必是对我的退魔能力心生畏惧 逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是还从未退过魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 人家小缠一直都在退魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早的报纸上还刊登了超大的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太打击人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好厉害 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比釜吉要可爱一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在扭屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在扭屁股 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把肚子露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把肚子露出来了 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它飘起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它飘起来了 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釜吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 发现奈兹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请批准我使用雷加利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 查清它的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不办不到 它只会说「mokyu」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,mokyu？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 mokyu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗许可下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 完成退魔少女使命的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没有那种使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早料到会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经准备好了我和你替换用的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么弄到我的衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又擅自进我家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是房东的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这叫霸道才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个外形不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统关闭 限制已解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维度变换 等级3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能落后 我也要变身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有听到我说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,985)}Photogenic Poasma Illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超美少女等离子幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这中地方战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把奈兹带到高次元然后消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变换 等级4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍电影 这是在拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 由麻？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的 奈兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该叫我由麻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你卖萌也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉她了呢 克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有伤到它的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻她们没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天遇到的奈兹又小又可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小家伙总不可能变出很多同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黏在一起变成大个子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\f60}是传说中的退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釜谷商业街发生大楼倒塌事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}釜谷商业街发生大楼倒塌事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大楼倒塌？
