Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成大灾难了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粘糊糊 好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让灾害进一步扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一击定胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭这种薄墙就想困住我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 又塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太危险了 根本无法靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然规模不同 这和昨天在原宿发生的事件一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这个束缚解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君 感谢你一直以来的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法成为退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法保护不大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 防御很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝之仇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其引向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭之路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的首胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着还没被卷入麻烦事 我先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就装做是受害者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的大意造成了这样的结果 我已经在反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 替换的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生 这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没得到进入现场的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你留在外面不就行了
