Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实不相瞒 我们把恶灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又来凑热闹了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说得没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是告诉过你不要去危险的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…
