Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:23:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起前去的海边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是充满了伸吾君和妈妈的回忆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 大海与温泉、偶有恶灵
